trans-unit.source: Describes a ClickOnce or native Win32 application manifest.

trans-unit.source: A token that represents a version of the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Et token som representerer en versjon av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer navnet på programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en samlingsreferansen som representerer inngangspunktet for applikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL of the error report.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URL-adresse for feilrapporten.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the URL of the error report.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder URL-adresse for feilrapporten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the file associations that are defined in the manifest.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir filen tilknytninger som er definert i manifestet.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the file associations.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder filen tilknytninger.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the application is hosted in a browser (as WPF Web Browser Applications are).
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om programmet ligger i en nettleser (som WPF webprogrammer nettleseren er).

trans-unit.source: For project types other than WPF Web Browser Applications, you should set HostInBrowser to `False` (the default value).
trans-unit.target: For prosjekttyper enn WPF webprogrammer nettleseren, må du angi HostInBrowser til `False` (standardverdien).

trans-unit.source: When you deploy a WPF Web Browser Application, you must set the HostInBrowser property to `True`.
trans-unit.target: Når du distribuerer en WPF nettleseren webprogram, må du angi egenskapen HostInBrowser til `True`.

trans-unit.source: This causes the `<hostInBrowser>` tag to be added to the generated application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Dette fører til at den `<hostInBrowser>` koden som skal legges til genererte programmanifest.

trans-unit.source: This tag enables ClickOnce to deploy projects for browser-hosted applications, which contain .xbap files.
trans-unit.target: Denne koden aktiverer ClickOnce å distribuere prosjektene for nettleser vertsbaserte programmer som inneholder .xbap filer.

trans-unit.source: You will also have to make the application available only online by setting <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.DeployManifest.Install%2A> to `False`.
trans-unit.target: Du har også gjøre programmet tilgjengelig bare Internett ved å angi <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.DeployManifest.Install%2A>til `False`.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.DeployManifest.Install%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not do this, you will receive [MSBuild Error MSB3116](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke gjør dette, får du [MSBuild feil MSB3116](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether the application being deployed will be hosted in a browser (<xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>), or not (<xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>).
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om programmet som distribueres lagres i en nettleser (<xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>), eller ikke (<xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> applies only to WPF Web Browser Applications.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>gjelder bare for WPF nettleseren webprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the program icon file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir ikonfilen programmet.

trans-unit.source: The program icon is expressed in the generated application manifest and is used for the **Start** menu and **Add or Remove Programs**.
trans-unit.target: Ikon for programmet er angitt i det genererte programmanifestet og brukes til den **Start** menyen og **Legg til eller fjern programmer**.

trans-unit.source: If this the icon file is not specified, a default icon is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ikonfilen ikke er angitt, brukes en default-ikonet.

trans-unit.source: For a native Win32 manifest, this input is ignored.
trans-unit.target: Inndataene ignoreres for en opprinnelig Win32-manifestet.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the name of the icon file.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer navnet på ikonfilen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the manifest is a ClickOnce application manifest or a native Win32 application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om manifestfilen er en ClickOnce-programmanifest eller en opprinnelig Win32-programmanifest.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether the manifest is a ClickOnce application manifest (<xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>) or a native Win32 manifest (<xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>).
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om manifestfilen er en ClickOnce-programmanifest (<xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>) eller et innebygd Win32-manifest (<xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the maximum allowed length of a file path in a ClickOnce application deployment.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir den maksimale tillatte lengden på en filbane i distribusjonen en ClickOnce-programmet.

trans-unit.source: If this value is specified, the length of each file path in the application is checked against this limit.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne verdien er angitt, kontrolleres lengden på hver filbane i applikasjonen mot denne grensen.

trans-unit.source: Any items that exceed the limit cause a warning message.
trans-unit.target: Alle elementer som overskrider grensen på føre til at en advarsel.

trans-unit.source: If this input is not specified or is zero, no checking is performed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis disse inndataene ikke er angitt eller er null, utføres ingen kontroll.

trans-unit.source: For a native Win32 manifest, this input is ignored.
trans-unit.target: Inndataene ignoreres for en opprinnelig Win32-manifestet.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the maximum allowed length of a file path in a ClickOnce application deployment.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir den maksimale tillatte lengden på en filbane i en ClickOnce programdistribusjon.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies a textual description for the operating system dependency.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir en beskrivelse for operativsystemet avhengighet.

trans-unit.source: A string that indicates the operating system dependency.
trans-unit.target: En tekststreng som angir avhengigheten operativsystemet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies a support URL for the operating system dependency.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir en URL-adresse for støtte for operativsystemet avhengighet.

trans-unit.source: A string indicating the support URL for the operating system dependency.
trans-unit.target: En tekststreng som angir URL-adressen for støtte for operativsystemet avhengighet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the minimum required operating system version required by the application.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir minimum nødvendig operativsystemversjonen kreves av programmet.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the minimum operating system version required by the application.
trans-unit.target: Angir minimumskrav for operativsystem-versjonen som kreves av programmet.

trans-unit.source: An example value is "5.1.2600.0" for Windows XP.
trans-unit.target: En eksempelverdi er "5.1.2600.0" for Windows XP.

trans-unit.source: If this input is not specified, a default value is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis disse inndataene ikke er angitt, brukes en standardverdi.

trans-unit.source: The default value is the minimum supported operating system of the .NET Framework, which is "4.10.0.0" for Windows 98SE.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er minimum støttet operativsystem for .NET Framework, som er "4.10.0.0" for Windows 98SE.

trans-unit.source: However, if the application contains any native or Reg-Free COM references, the default is Windows XP.
trans-unit.target: Hvis programmet inneholder opprinnelig eller Reg uten COM refererer til, er standard Windows XP.

trans-unit.source: For a native Win32 manifest, this input is ignored.
trans-unit.target: Inndataene ignoreres for en opprinnelig Win32-manifestet.

trans-unit.source: A string that indicates the minimum required operating system version required by the application.
trans-unit.target: En tekststreng som angir minimum nødvendig operativsystemversjonen kreves av programmet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the <xref uid="langword_csharp_ProductName" name="ProductName" href=""></xref> property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_ProductName" name="ProductName" href=""> </xref> egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `ProductName` property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen samsvarer med den `ProductName` egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: The default is null.
trans-unit.target: Standard er null.

trans-unit.source: If `ProductName` is null and <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A> is `True`, the RegisteredOrganization value in the registry is written to the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `ProductName` er null og <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A>er `True`, RegisteredOrganization-verdi i registret skrives til programmanifestet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A>

trans-unit.source: If RegisteredOrganization is also null, the assembly name is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis RegisteredOrganization også er null, brukes navnet på samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A string value that corresponds to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_ProductName" name="ProductName" href=""></xref> property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: En strengverdi som tilsvarer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_ProductName" name="ProductName" href=""> </xref> egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_PublisherName" name="PublisherName" href=""> </xref> egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `PublisherName` property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen samsvarer med den `PublisherName` egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: The default is null.
trans-unit.target: Standard er null.

trans-unit.source: If `PublisherName` is null and <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A> is `True`, the assembly name is written to the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `PublisherName` er null og <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A>er `True`, samlingsnavnet skrives til programmanifestet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string value that corresponds to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_PublisherName" name="PublisherName" href=""></xref> property in the project file.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the suite name.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder navnet på serien.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the <xref uid="langword_csharp_SupportUrl" name="SupportUrl" href=""></xref> property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir den <xref uid="langword_csharp_SupportUrl" name="SupportUrl" href=""> </xref> egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `SupportUrl` property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen samsvarer med den `SupportUrl` egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: The default is null.
trans-unit.target: Standard er null.

trans-unit.source: If `SupportUrl` is null and <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A> is `True`, an empty string is written to the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `SupportUrl` er null og <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A>er `True`, en tom streng skrives til programmanifestet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.UseApplicationTrust%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string value that corresponds to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_SupportUrl" name="SupportUrl" href=""></xref> property in the project file.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Product*>, <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Publisher*>, and <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl*> properties are written to the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om den <> </> *>, <> </> *>, og <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl*>Egenskaper som skrives til programmanifestet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl*>

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Product%2A>, <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Publisher%2A>, and <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl%2A> properties are set to null.
trans-unit.target: Som standard i <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Product%2A>, <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Publisher%2A>, og <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl%2A>egenskapene er angitt til null.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl%2A> </xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Publisher%2A> </xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Product%2A>

trans-unit.source: They are used only if UseApplicationTrust is `True`.
trans-unit.target: De brukes bare hvis UseApplicationTrust `True`.

trans-unit.source: If this property is `True`, the values of these properties are written to the corresponding tags in the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er `True`, verdiene for disse egenskapene er skrevet til de tilsvarende kodene i programmanifestet.

trans-unit.source: If UseApplicationTrust is `False` (the default value), these properties are ignored.
trans-unit.target: Hvis UseApplicationTrust `False` (standardverdien) disse egenskapene ignoreres.

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `UseApplicationTrust` property in the project file.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen samsvarer med den `UseApplicationTrust` egenskap i prosjektfilen.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Publisher*>, <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.Product*>, and <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl*> properties are written to the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om den <> </> *>, <> </> *>, og <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl*>Egenskaper som skrives til programmanifestet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.SupportUrl*>

trans-unit.source: If the value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>, they are written to the application manifest.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""> </xref>, de som skrives til programmanifestet.

trans-unit.source: If the value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""></xref>, these properties are ignored.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_False" name="False" href=""> </xref>, ignoreres disse egenskapene.

trans-unit.source: Performs various checks to verify the validity of the manifest.
trans-unit.target: Utfører forskjellige kontroller for å bekrefte gyldigheten av manifestet.

trans-unit.source: Any resulting errors or warnings are reported in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.OutputMessageCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Resulterende feil eller advarsler rapporteres i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.OutputMessageCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Before calling this method, you must set the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.TargetFrameworkVersion%2A> property so that the validation can verify application manifest against the correct version of the .NET Framework runtime.
trans-unit.target: Før du kaller opp denne metoden, må du angi den <xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.TargetFrameworkVersion%2A>egenskapen slik at valideringen kan kontrollere programmanifest mot riktig versjon av .NET Framework runtime.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Tasks.Deployment.ManifestUtilities.ApplicationManifest.TargetFrameworkVersion%2A>
